require ''xcodeproj''
project_path = ''MyTodoApp.xcodeproj''
project = Xcodeproj::Project.open(project_path)
target = project.targets.first
group = project.main_group[''MyTodoApp'']

files_to_add = [
  ''MainTabBarController.swift'',
  ''HomeViewController.swift'',
  ''AccountDetailsViewController.swift'',
  ''CardDetailsViewController.swift'',
  ''WealthViewController.swift'',
  ''WealthOnboardingViewController.swift'',
  ''LoanOnboardingViewController.swift'',
  ''RewardsListViewController.swift'',
  ''TransferPayViewController.swift'',
  ''ServicesViewController.swift'',
  ''ExploreViewController.swift''
]

files_to_add.each do |filename|
  file_path = ""MyTodoApp/#{filename}""
  unless target.source_build_phase.files.any? { |f| f.file_ref&.path == filename }
    file_ref = group.new_reference(filename)
    target.add_file_references([file_ref])
    puts ""Added #{filename}""
  else
    puts ""#{filename} already exists""
  end
end

project.save
puts ''Project saved successfully!''
")
